org.sakaiproject.content.impl.serialize.api

Interface SerializableCollectionAccess

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseContentService.BaseCollectionEdit, SAXSerializableCollectionAccess

    public interface SerializableCollectionAccess
     This is an accessor interface for the Collection to enable the searializer to do its work
 All methods should be straight getters and setters with no logic.

    ieb
